\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {13.5}{\ignorespaces Menores de la primera fila: al eliminar la fila $1$ y la columna $j$ (gris) queda la submatriz $M_{1j}$ (azul); $\det (A)=a_{11}\det (M_{11})-a_{12}\det (M_{12})+a_{13}\det (M_{13})$.}}{278}{figure.13.5}%
